Package: snapcrackleprop
Title: Count and Calculate Proportions in Group(s)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Renessa", "Gomes", email = "rengomes@student.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This is a package containing a single function that summarizes the 
  count and proportion of observations that meet one or more conditions within 
  given group(s) of a data frame.
